       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI83104.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI83104.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Manuten誽o Niveis de Aprova誽o                             *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI83104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6600 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0104 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV8310.
       COPY COCV8311.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT6600 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6600'.
           05 CON-ARVT0104 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT0104'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-USER      PIC X(20).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI83104'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI83104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV8310-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8310-ASE               TO COCV8311-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV8310-NIDPROJECTO ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV8310-NIDPROJECTO   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8310-ADE               TO COCV8311-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2299-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-INSERE-DADOS
                 THRU 2399-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE COCV8310-CUSER01 TO WS-USER
              PERFORM 2250-VALIDA-USER
                 THRU 2250-VALIDA-USER-EXIT
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV8311-CUSER01-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-USER-N-EXISTS
                   TO COCV8311-CUSER01-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV8311-CUSER01-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV8310-CUSER02 NOT = SPACES
              MOVE COCV8310-CUSER02 TO WS-USER
              PERFORM 2250-VALIDA-USER
                 THRU 2250-VALIDA-USER-EXIT
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV8311-CUSER02-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-USER-N-EXISTS
                   TO COCV8311-CUSER02-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV8311-CUSER02-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2299-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2250-VALIDA-USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2250-VALIDA-USER.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2250-VALIDA-USER    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-USER TO ARCD0104-GUSERNAME.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       GUSERNAME
                    ,  ISTATUS
                 INTO
                       :ARCD0104-GUSERNAME
                    ,  :ARCD0104-ISTATUS
                  FROM  ARVT0104
                 WHERE  GUSERNAME = :ARCD0104-GUSERNAME
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT0104 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2250-VALIDA-USER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-INSERE-DADOS.
      *-------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-INSERE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-INSERE-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8310-NIDPROJECTO     TO COCD6600-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV8310-CUSER01         TO COCD6600-CUSER01.
           MOVE COCV8310-CUSER02         TO COCD6600-CUSER02.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I      TO COCD6600-CUSERID.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS

           EXEC SQL
                INSERT INTO COVT6600
                (
                   NIDPROJECTO
                 , CUSER01
                 , CUSER02
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST
                )
                VALUES (
                       :COCD6600-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD6600-CUSER01
                     , :COCD6600-CUSER02
                     , :COCD6600-CUSERID
                     ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                )
           END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT6600 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-DUPREC
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                      MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO COCV8311-NIDPROJECTO-S
                      MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-A-EXISTS
                        TO COCV8311-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                      MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                        TO COCV8311-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
                    IF NOT DB2-OK
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2399-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8311-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV8311-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8311-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
